Check 3FGL classification results based on 4FGL new discovery

Out of 3033 3FGL sources, 469 are missing in 4FGL for various reasons.

Important variables:

  • Variability Index
  • Curvature
  • Hardneww Ratio [Ackerman et al.Â 2012]:

\(hr_{ij} = \frac{EnergyFlux_j - EnergyFlux_i} {EnergyFlux_j + EnergyFlux_i}\), where

\(EnergyFlux_{i}\) is log photon flux in energy bands. hr = -1 for very soft source (high \(EnergyFlux_j = 0\)), +1 for very hard source (low \(EnergyFlux_i = 0\))

In plot variabiltiy vs.Â curvature, pulsars (\(\bigtriangleup\)) in bottom-right corner, with curved spectrum and low variability. Misclassifications (red) are low variability sources

In plot variabiltiy vs.Â hr45, pulsars (\(\bigtriangleup\)) are in bottom-left corner, soft in hr45 (energy band 1~3GeV vs.Â 3~10GeV)

1. 3FGL Unassociated sources with significance > 10

FGL3_unassoc_signif_res <- FGL3_results %>%
        filter(CLASS1 == "") %>%
        filter(Signif > 10) %>%       #>10: 149 obs
        filter(LR_Pred==RF_Pred) %>%
        # filter(LR_Pred=="PSR") %>%
        arrange(desc(Signif)) 

FGL3_unassoc_res_FGL4 <- inner_join(FGL3_unassoc_signif_res, FGL4_tidy_for_FGL3,
                                    by = c("Source_Name" = "FGL3_Source_name")) %>% #>10: 108
                         filter (CLASS1.y != "" | CLASS2 != "")  #>10: 48
FGL3_unassoc_res_FGL4 <- FGL3_unassoc_res_FGL4[ -c(8,9) ]

FGL3_accuracy_pred <- mutate(FGL3_unassoc_res_FGL4, 
       accurate=(FGL3_unassoc_res_FGL4$LR_Pred==FGL3_unassoc_res_FGL4$class))
ncol <- ncol(FGL3_accuracy_pred)
FGL3_accuracy_pred<- FGL3_accuracy_pred[c(ncol,ncol-1,ncol-10, 1:(ncol-11), (ncol-9):(ncol-2))]

table(FGL3_accuracy_pred$class, FGL3_accuracy_pred$accurate)
##        
##         FALSE TRUE
##   AGN       5   17
##   PSR       1   19
##   Other     6    0
table(FGL3_accuracy_pred$CLASS1.y, FGL3_accuracy_pred$accurate)

##        FALSE TRUE
##            1    0

2. 3FGL Unassociated sources with significance > 4 (Whole Catalog)

FGL3_unassoc_results <- FGL3_results %>%
        filter(CLASS1 == "") %>%
        filter(Signif > 4) %>%      #4: 921 obs
        filter(LR_Pred==RF_Pred) %>%
        # filter(LR_Pred=="PSR") %>%
        arrange(desc(Signif))

FGL3_unassoc_res_FGL4_all <- inner_join(FGL3_unassoc_results, FGL4_tidy_for_FGL3,
                                    by = c("Source_Name" = "FGL3_Source_name")) %>% #>4: 566
                             filter (CLASS1.y != "" | CLASS2 != "") #315
FGL3_unassoc_res_FGL4_all <- FGL3_unassoc_res_FGL4_all[ -c(8,9) ]

FGL3_accuracy_pred_all <- mutate(FGL3_unassoc_res_FGL4_all, 
                        accurate=(FGL3_unassoc_res_FGL4_all$LR_Pred==FGL3_unassoc_res_FGL4_all$class))
FGL3_accuracy_pred_all<- FGL3_accuracy_pred_all[c(ncol,ncol-1,ncol-10, 1:(ncol-11), (ncol-9):(ncol-2))]
